- Create a Cart Page in Shopify using JSON templates

✅ Step 1: Create Cart Template (JSON)
File: templates/cart.json
1) Go to your Shopify Admin > Online Store > Themes > Edit Code.
2) Under Templates, click "Add a new template" → choose cart → type: JSON.

{
  "sections": {
    "main-cart": {
      "type": "main-cart"
    }
  },
  "order": ["main-cart"]
}


✅ Step 2: Create Section
File: sections/main-cart.liquid

Note: Code in 1.2 file.
